🛡️ AI Phishing Detection Platform

A Python-based backend system for detecting phishing URLs, emails, and suspicious text using cybersecurity APIs, rule-based analysis, and risk scoring.
This project demonstrates real-world backend development with authentication, scanning modules, dashboards, and admin analytics.

🚀 Features
🔐 Authentication
User registration & login
JWT-based secure authentication
Role-based access (User / Admin)
🔍 Phishing Detection
🌐 URL scanning for phishing websites
📧 Email content analysis
📝 Text-based scam detection
Risk scoring system (LOW / MEDIUM / HIGH)
📊 Dashboard
Total scan statistics
Risk distribution charts
Recent scan history
Monthly scan analytics
🧑‍💼 Admin Panel
View all users
Monitor system scans
Access activity logs
View reports & analytics
📄 Reports System
Generate security reports per scan
Export reports as PDF
Export reports as CSV
📜 Activity Logging
Track user actions
Store scan history
Security event monitoring
🏗️ Tech Stack
Backend: Python (FastAPI / Flask)
Database: PostgreSQL / Supabase
Authentication: JWT (JSON Web Token)
Security APIs:
VirusTotal API
Google Safe Browsing API
Deployment: Render / Railway / Docker
📁 Project Structure
backend/
│
├── routes/          # API routes
├── controllers/     # Business logic
├── services/        # External API integrations
├── models/          # Database models
├── middleware/      # Auth & security middleware
├── utils/           # Helper functions
├── config/          # Config files
⚙️ API Endpoints
🔐 Authentication
POST /api/v1/auth/register
POST /api/v1/auth/login
POST /api/v1/auth/token
GET  /api/v1/users/me
🔍 Scans
POST /api/v1/scans/url
POST /api/v1/scans/email
POST /api/v1/scans/text

GET  /api/v1/scans
GET  /api/v1/scans/{scan_id}
GET  /api/v1/scans/search/{keyword}
📊 Dashboard
GET /api/v1/dashboard/stats
GET /api/v1/dashboard/recent-scans
GET /api/v1/dashboard/risk-distribution
GET /api/v1/dashboard/monthly-scans
🧑‍💼 Admin
GET /api/v1/admin/dashboard
GET /api/v1/admin/users
GET /api/v1/admin/scans
GET /api/v1/admin/reports
GET /api/v1/admin/activities
📄 Reports
POST /api/v1/reports/generate/{scan_id}
GET  /api/v1/reports
GET  /api/v1/reports/{report_id}

POST /api/v1/reports/export/pdf/{report_id}
POST /api/v1/reports/export/csv/{report_id}
📜 Activity
GET /api/v1/activity
🧠 How It Works
User submits URL/email/text
Backend validates input
Data sent to:
Rule-based detection engine
VirusTotal API
Google Safe Browsing API
System generates:
Risk score (0–100)
Risk level (LOW / MEDIUM / HIGH)
Final classification (SAFE / PHISHING)
Result stored in database
Dashboard & reports updated
📦 Installation
# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/your-username/phishing-detection-platform.git

# Move into project
cd phishing-detection-platform

# Create virtual environment
python -m venv venv

# Activate environment
# Windows:
venv\Scripts\activate

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt
▶️ Run the Project
uvicorn main:app --reload

Then open:

http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs
🔐 Environment Variables

Create .env file:

DATABASE_URL=your_database_url
SECRET_KEY=your_secret_key
JWT_ALGORITHM=HS256

VIRUSTOTAL_API_KEY=your_api_key
GOOGLE_SAFE_BROWSING_API_KEY=your_api_key
